snippet.title: Surviving Mars Green Planet Feature Breakdown Part 2
snippet.description:
Mark your calendars for the release of Green Planet on May 16th! Terraforming, new buildings, vegetation, and more are coming to Mars, as you transform the planet into a new home for humankind, a Green Planet

Follow us on the forums and social media for Dev Diaries, Live Streams, Tutorials, and more!

https://www.facebook.com/SurvivingMarsGame/
https://twitter.com/Surviving_Mars
